headline: The Weight Loss Drug Market Has Gotten Messy. What to Know.
summary: Compounded weight loss drugs have been mostly off the market for about a month, but the weight loss drug industry remains as unsettled as ever.  Earlier this week,  Novo Nordisk   tore up a partnership with the telehealth storefront  Hims & Hers Health  which had allowed Hims to sell the Novo weight loss drug Wegovy at a lower price for cash-paying patients.
